      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know... i've tried. but it just feels like people don't get it. they want to 'fix' me like i'm some problem to be solved. but it's not a phase, it's just... empty. i'm so exhausted from trying to find a reason to keep going when the only thing that made it worth it is gone. sometimes it really feels like the only way to actually find some peace is to just stop fighting. to just let go.",
