      "content": "it's just that \"letting go\" sounds so much easier than this constant struggle. like, why am i even forced to endure this pain when there's no end in sight? it feels more like a trap than a life at this point. it honestly feels like the only way to actually be still and not feel this aching is to just... not be here anymore. does that even make sense?",
